WEBVTT

00:00.038 --> 00:01.718
<i>Previously on When Calls the Heart...</i>

00:01.744 --> 00:02.633
What do you think, Laura?

00:02.658 --> 00:03.828
Yes to being your nanny.

00:03.852 --> 00:05.055
Fiona Miller.

00:05.080 --> 00:06.552
I operate the telephone switchboard.

00:06.577 --> 00:08.578
Rosemary, there is no me and Carson

00:08.603 --> 00:10.218
except as doctor and nurse.

00:10.243 --> 00:12.568
There is definitely a spark
between you and Carson.

00:12.594 --> 00:14.273
<i>You two are perfect for each other.</i>

00:14.298 --> 00:16.018
Bill, you have been in a mood all week.

00:16.050 --> 00:17.692
This wouldn't have anything
to do with you losing out

00:17.717 --> 00:18.885
on the saloon, would it?

00:18.910 --> 00:20.938
This guy just swoops in out of nowhere?

00:20.963 --> 00:23.578
This new saloon owner sounds
like a rogue and a scoundrel.

00:23.603 --> 00:25.554
You wouldn't happen
to be this new owner,

00:25.579 --> 00:26.569
by any chance?

00:26.594 --> 00:28.904
Lucas Bouchard at your service.

